official_title: A bill to designate certain lands in the Snoqualmie and Wenatchee National Forests, Washington as "Alpine Lakes Wilderness" and "Enchantment Wilderness" for inclusion in the national wilderness preservation system.

summary.text: Directs the Secretary of Agriculture to designate specified lands in the Snoqualmie and Wenatchee National Forests, Washington, as Alpine Lakes Wilderness and Enchantment Wilderness for inclusion in the national wilderness preservation system.

titles.title: A bill to designate certain lands in the Snoqualmie and Wenatchee National Forests, Washington as "Alpine Lakes Wilderness" and "Enchantment Wilderness" for inclusion in the national wilderness preservation system.
